channel.title: RuneLine 2015 Updated
channel.description:
Hello all, I'm just here to post a topic on a server I have been playing the last year or two. Just recently they have remade the server practically :) & I'm in love. I am a donator ( Mannie ) you can add the owner ( Fate ) Please feel free to watch the promotion video https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yh6PP-GbSmY http://runeline.com/ http://runeline.com/forums/
No fuss direct download 900kb+ http://runeline.com/Runeline.jar
Feel completely free to contact me on forum or in game. I don't have a lot of information about the server other then the video, if you have any question I suggest you try the forums. Thanks for your time & please take the time to try the new server updated. :) :) :)
